      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly start? This vehicle is ready for someone with a vision! While it shows significant wear and will require some mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for a restoration enthusiast or anyone looking for a great value on a fixer-upper. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own!",
