    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade specimen that serves as a time capsule for the model. This vehicle has been exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment, preserving the factory paint\u2019s deep-gloss finish without a single stone chip, swirl mark, or blemish. The interior is equally pristine; the leather remains supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are protected by original mats, and it retains that distinct showroom aroma. Every electronic feature, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history with a recent comprehensive fluid flush and a fresh set of premium tires. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously maintained investment. I welcome and encourage independent pre-purchase inspections to verify its exceptional state.",
      "price": 47900.0,
